analysis.description:
DcorpProxy.execute (/unique_contracts/0x01d5d0108589f3c52fcce6e65503bb6515e66698.sol#802-830) uses a dangerous strict equality:
	- assert(bool)(balanceBefore + balanceToSend == _acceptedAddress.balance)
	- assert(bool)(this.balance == 0)

TokenRetriever.retrieveTokens (/unique_contracts/0x01d5d0108589f3c52fcce6e65503bb6515e66698.sol#216-233) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-tokenInstance.transfer(msg.sender,tokenBalance) (/unique_contracts/0x01d5d0108589f3c52fcce6e65503bb6515e66698.sol#228-231)
